original_title: Family Star (The Mutt & Jeff Icecream Sundae + Mothman)
overview: Various different holiday locations ar joined together through the pleasures of ice cream in The Mutt & Jeff Icecream Sundae, while in Mothman the strange title character crawls through roof-top windows and we see footage of a funfair. These two films have many similarities with the other Keen diary movies but have always been shown in this pairing, and under this title.
title: Family Star (The Mutt & Jeff Icecream Sundae + Mothman)
